71
00:06:28.564 --> 00:06:30.023
Semoga beruntung.

72
00:07:09.396 --> 00:07:13.692
Jofi, kau dengar seseorang
di depan pintu?


73
00:07:14.443 --> 00:07:15.444
Jofi?

74
00:07:20.115 --> 00:07:22.326
- Dr.Freud.
